{"tid":1429411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀太空館有火 ！","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:43:40.000Z","uid":135798,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a34c7b03953254779ce7639fe8e853ab2f9c068","tid":1429411,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9PdAbN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9PdAbN.gif&h=e677c4c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e1e871be31ba886d893c87dadec70f1217ed0dc","tid":1429411,"uid":276558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9316a6aafb3394360c1edaaa729dc79cecb09cef","tid":1429411,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"仲有火焰圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e383b079a3c402b57d5f083f5efde913c3563cc","tid":1429411,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7645e88d5e7c068975a0bccb77208c4bbacdf999","tid":1429411,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"多咗好多人買雷射筆，求推Post: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【極重要】請立即停止漫罵及用雷射筆射向拍照的途人/大廈單位<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418134</a>"},{"pid":"2889470799e01e8a2762c594b74d92d3cc14aa38","tid":1429411,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a34c7b03953254779ce7639fe8e853ab2f9c068","tid":1429411,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9PdAbN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9PdAbN.gif&h=e677c4c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c6f3ae2237732ae9344f857731f8f4aff5a0d2","tid":1429411,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3eb770be7114d7c3119d5363151dc13bc9f8b53a","tid":1429411,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1470368b0a6581c414e27e164568f940821ded3","tid":1429411,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:32:24.000Z","msg":"強烈要求警務人員喺記者會進行示範！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n借位推"},{"pid":"7469fb5c49427c697cee6d6b04c7088ff0877db6","tid":1429411,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6d42337b7363937e06d38a4e90c273cae5e78c","tid":1429411,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30a1b126eebca9bca0be8660515ade2a588ee36","tid":1429411,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}